WEBVTT

00:00:04.264 --> 00:00:06.193
THIS IS TAPE THREE

00:00:06.193 --> 00:00:08.159
OF AN INTERVIEW WITH

00:00:08.159 --> 00:00:10.805
MISTER MOYSEY SHNEYDER

00:00:10.845 --> 00:00:14.332
ON OCTOBER NINTH, NINETEEN NINETY SIX

00:00:15.047 --> 00:00:16.259
INTERVIEWEE

00:00:16.259 --> 00:00:18.402
BY RAE MELTZER.

00:00:22.405 --> 00:00:23.563
dos iz

00:00:24.075 --> 00:00:26.752
gekumen tsu forn fun Brazil

00:00:27.130 --> 00:00:28.913
dem tatn's a bruder.

00:00:29.104 --> 00:00:31.545
zey hobn finf un fertsik yor

00:00:31.753 --> 00:00:34.227
nit gezen zikh eyner mit di andere.

00:00:35.926 --> 00:00:38.092
un dernokh, nokhn krig

00:00:38.318 --> 00:00:39.800
nayntsn eyn un f-

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:42.514
fir un, finf un fertsik.

00:00:43.245 --> 00:00:46.660
fun der ershter vayb zayn zun hot geforn in Erets-Yisroel

00:00:46.660 --> 00:00:48.595
fun dortn hot er aroysgezukht

00:00:49.270 --> 00:00:50.664
zayn familye

00:00:51.177 --> 00:00:54.546
un me hot zikh, oykh gekumen tsu forn tsu undz in Rusland

00:00:54.788 --> 00:00:57.769
vu zey hobn zikh gezen zikh iber finf un fertsiktn yor.

00:00:58.045 --> 00:01:00.249
dos bin ikh mit der vayb

00:01:00.593 --> 00:01:01.939
un der zun

00:01:01.939 --> 00:01:03.219
mit der tokhter

00:01:03.225 --> 00:01:04.586
un mayn tate

00:01:05.470 --> 00:01:06.982
mit dem feter.

00:01:11.123 --> 00:01:12.298
nayntsn

00:01:13.823 --> 00:01:15.268
EIGHTY FIVE,

00:01:15.426 --> 00:01:17.597
di tokhter hot khasene gehat far

00:01:18.379 --> 00:01:19.621
THIS MAN.

00:01:20.134 --> 00:01:23.722
itstert lebn zey do in Amerike un zeyer danken

00:01:24.133 --> 00:01:25.173
alemen.

00:01:27.930 --> 00:01:28.734
⟨FINISHED⟩.

00:01:32.925 --> 00:01:34.117
dos iz

00:01:34.427 --> 00:01:36.463
gekumen tsu forn tsu mir

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:38.825
aher in BALTIMORE shoyn.

00:01:39.135 --> 00:01:40.971
er iz gekumen frier far mir,

00:01:40.971 --> 00:01:42.127
mayn bruder

00:01:42.127 --> 00:01:43.281
mitn zun

00:01:44.333 --> 00:01:47.347
un dos iz di iberike mayn familye, ikh, di vayb,

00:01:47.995 --> 00:01:50.807
di tokhter mit di eyniklekh mitn man.

00:01:52.045 --> 00:01:53.119
⟨FINISHED⟩.

00:01:56.922 --> 00:01:58.131
dos iz

00:01:58.305 --> 00:02:01.910
iber fuftsn yor hob ikh zikh bagegnt zikh mit dem bruder.

00:02:02.052 --> 00:02:03.784
er iz avekgeforn in

00:02:03.975 --> 00:02:06.551
nayntsn zibn un nayn

00:02:06.895 --> 00:02:09.859
aher in Amerike, un er hot mir geshikt

00:02:10.675 --> 00:02:13.014
azoy ⟨zol⟩ ikh kenen kumen aher tsu im.

00:02:13.932 --> 00:02:17.548
iz hot er gekumen aher tsu forn in BALTIMORE, un do hobn mir zikh

00:02:17.548 --> 00:02:18.853
bagegnt zikh

00:02:19.112 --> 00:02:20.810
un geforn oyfn

00:02:21.103 --> 00:02:23.966
tsum yam, un dortn gemakht a PICTURE.

00:02:24.023 --> 00:02:27.378
mit mayn gantser fa- familye, di vos lebn do in BALTIMORE.
